      "text": "A tiny mouse lived near a big lion.\nOne day, the lion caught the mouse.\n\"Please let me go,\" said the mouse.\nThe lion laughed, but he let the mouse go.\nLater, the lion was trapped in a net.\nThe mouse chewed the ropes until the lion was free.\nEven small friends can help in big ways.",
      "questions": [
        {
          "q": "Why did the mouse chew the net?",
          "type": "mcq",
          "options": [
            {
              "t": "To free the lion",
              "c": true,
              "f": "Yes\u2014the mouse helped the lion escape."
            },
            {
              "t": "To eat the lion's food",
              "c": false,
              "f": "No\u2014he chewed the ropes."
            },
            {
              "t": "To build a house",
              "c": false,
              "f": "Not in this story."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "q": "What is the lesson of the story?",
          "type": "mcq",
          "options": [
            {
              "t": "Small friends can help too",
              "c": true,
              "f": "Correct\u2014that\u2019s the message."
            },
            {
              "t": "Never help anyone",
              "c": false,
              "f": "Opposite of the message."
            },
            {
              "t": "Lions can fly",
              "c": false,
              "f": "Not true."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
