      "text": "A fast hare boasted that he could run quicker than anyone.\nA tortoise said, \"Let\u2019s race.\"\nThe hare raced ahead and stopped to rest.\nThe tortoise walked slowly, step by step.\nThe hare fell asleep.\nThe tortoise kept going until he crossed the finish line.\nSlow and steady can win when you keep going.",
      "questions": [
        {
          "q": "What did the hare do during the race?",
          "type": "mcq",
          "options": [
            {
              "t": "He rested and fell asleep",
              "c": true,
              "f": "Yes\u2014he stopped and slept."
            },
            {
              "t": "He walked the whole way",
              "c": false,
              "f": "No\u2014he ran ahead then rested."
            },
            {
              "t": "He carried the tortoise",
              "c": false,
              "f": "No\u2014never happened."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "q": "Who won the race?",
          "type": "mcq",
          "options": [
            {
              "t": "The tortoise",
              "c": true,
              "f": "Correct\u2014steady steps won."
            },
            {
              "t": "The hare",
              "c": false,
              "f": "No\u2014the hare slept."
            },
            {
              "t": "No one",
              "c": false,
              "f": "Someone did win."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
